sp;website provides a secure shopping and browsing environment (SSL encryption) with Geotrust.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>TRADEMARK:</strong></h3><p><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/icons/t2_tradeMK2.jpg" alt="WORSHIP WARRIORS is trademarked" width="230" height="153"><br>WORSHIP WARRIORS ® is registered with the U.S. Patent and Trademark Office (USPTO).</p><ul><li>The Trademark provides nationwide notice of ownership of the mark.</li><li>The Trademark gives the licensee (WORSHIP WARRIORS) rights to institute legal. proceedings in the event of infringement.</li></ul>